<HEAD>
Active ingredient: 0.1% w/v hexetidine
</HEAD>


<BLOCK>
Hexetidine is a substance that kills bacteria and certain fungi. When used in a mouthwash, these properties are useful for the relief of mouth and throat infections.
</BLOCK>

